# barrelmania-updates

An update application written for the Run4Hope.  Run4Hope is a charity barrel race to benefit
the Hope Equestrian Center.  http://www.hopeequestrian.com 

## Core Application Stack

_This app is 100% serverless._

* Zappa Framework
* Flask
* Lambda
* SNS
* S3


### Features

* Text message subscriptions
* Live updates to the race

* TODO : Add donation funnels.

